cs.NI, cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.GR 

The paper discusses the challenges and enablers of wireless interconnected virtual reality, which involves networking, multimedia, computer vision, artificial intelligence, and graphics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture), followed by cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.GR (Graphics).
